    <name>QMPlay2</name>
    <summary>Video and audio player</summary>
    <description>
        <p>
            QMPlay2 is a video and audio player. It can play all formats supported by FFmpeg, libmodplug (including J2B and SFX).
            It also supports Audio CD, raw files, Rayman 2 music and chiptunes. It contains YouTube and MyFreeMP3 browser.
        </p>
    </description>
